{
  "info": {
    "name": "Fernandes Surgical CRM API",
    "description": "Coleção completa de APIs do CRM Fernandes Surgical\n\n## Autenticação\nTodas as APIs requerem JWT token no header Authorization.\n\n## Como usar:\n1. Execute primeiro a requisição \"Auth - Login\" para obter o token\n2. O token será salvo automaticamente na variável {{jwt_token}}\n3. Use as outras requisições normalmente\n\n## Variáveis necessárias:\n- base_url: https://rzzzfprgnoywmmjwepzm.supabase.co\n- anon_key: eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpc3MiOiJzdXBhYmFzZSIsInJlZiI6InJ6enpmcHJnbm95d21tandlcHptIiwicm9sZSI6ImFub24iLCJpYXQiOjE3NTkyNTMxODksImV4cCI6MjA3NDgyOTE4OX0.GVeAOtDEqJeev7dnDyemdj-W5WXZJdWZo-wUcCXx4wc",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "fernandes-surgical-crm"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Authentication",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Auth - Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "// Salvar o token JWT automaticamente",
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.environment.set(\"jwt_token\", jsonData.access_token);",
                  "    console.log(\"Token JWT salvo com sucesso!\");",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "apikey",
                "value": "{{anon_key}}",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"egles.vieiraa@gmail.com\",\n  \"password\": \"sua-senha-aqui\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/v1/token?grant_type=password",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "auth",
                "v1",
                "token"
              ],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "grant_type",
                  "value": "password"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Faz login e obtém o token JWT.\n\n**IMPORTANTE**: Altere o email e senha antes de executar.\n\nO token será salvo automaticamente na variável `jwt_token` para uso nas outras requisições."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Auth - Refresh Token",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "// Salvar o novo token JWT",
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.environment.set(\"jwt_token\", jsonData.access_token);",
                  "    pm.environment.set(\"refresh_token\", jsonData.refresh_token);",
                  "    console.log(\"Token renovado com sucesso!\");",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "apikey",
                "value": "{{anon_key}}",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"refresh_token\": \"{{refresh_token}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/v1/token?grant_type=refresh_token",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "auth",
                "v1",
                "token"
              ],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "grant_type",
                  "value": "refresh_token"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Renova o token JWT usando o refresh_token.\n\nUse quando o token expirar (após 1 hora)."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Auth - Get User",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "apikey",
                "value": "{{anon_key}}",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{jwt_token}}",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/v1/user",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "auth",
                "v1",
                "user"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Retorna informações do usuário autenticado.\n\nÚtil para verificar se o token está válido."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ],
      "description": "Endpoints de autenticação do Supabase"
    },
